195
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:07,000
 a ovi šest dana naučili su me discipliniranosti, organizaciji

196
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:13,000
 prilagođavanje vremenu i oslanjanje na gospodina

197
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:18,000
