00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,000
 ok

309
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:26,000
 drugi problem

310
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:29,000
 pre malo smo prisutni u ovome svijetu

311
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:32,000
 evo gospodin kaže

